title: Soon You'll Get Better
description:
Taylor shared this deeply emotional song and swore that she would never perform it, but she did whenever the world needed it the most! What is this song about? Amy, Lacey, Ana and Nick break it down!
What did we miss? What would you like to hear from us? Let us know!
